Precondition:
1. install tomcat
    brew install tomcat
2. change config to different port and webapps root
    add config to $CATALINA_HOME/conf/server.xml
        <!-- configure by linjun -->
        <Service name="linjunService">
            <Connector port="8081" protocol="org.apache.coyote.http11.Http11NioProtocol"
                connectionTimeout="20000"
                redirectPort="8443" />
            <Engine name="Catalina" defaultHost="localhost">
                <Host name="localhost"  appBase="linjunWebApps"
                unpackWARs="true" autoDeploy="true">
                </Host>
            </Engine>
        </Service>

Deploy to tomcat
    deploy.sh


Be ware:
    Migration from earlier version to >4.0: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/wiki/Migrating-from-earlier-versions-of-the-spring-framework#enforced-minimum-dependency-versions


